---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
	<section class="text-center py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-white rounded-3xl mb-12">
		<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">
			Unlocking the Secrets of <span class="text-indigo-600">Memory</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
			We are a diverse group of researchers, engineers, and thinkers dedicated to exploring memory systems in humans, machines, and society.
		</p>
		<div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
			<a href="/research" class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
				Explore Research
			</a>
			<a href="/about" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-indigo-600 font-medium rounded-lg border border-indigo-200 hover:bg-indigo-50 transition shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
				Learn More
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
		<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition">
			<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
				</svg>
			</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Biological Memory</h3>
			<p class="text-gray-600">Investigating the neural mechanisms underlying encoding, storage, and retrieval in the brain.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition">
			<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
				</svg>
			</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Artificial Systems</h3>
			<p class="text-gray-600">Developing novel architectures for long-term storage and retrieval in AI models.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition">
			<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 text-teal-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
				</svg>
			</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Collective Memory</h3>
			<p class="text-gray-600">Analyzing how societies remember and forget information over time.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>